snippet.textDisplay:
*lines up an ice cube on the snowmans hat*
*triggers divebomb*
*smashes ice-cube*
*Hits ground hard, bounces off -- flies clean off the hat-- loses two honeycomb pieces*
*falls about 15 stories into pool of freezing water -- cant fly*
*hits so hard that I lose 4 honeycomb pieces*
*O_O OMG ONE LIFE LEFT!*
*freezing water hits for one honeycomb piece*
*damn it*

When this happened, me and my friends were rolling around laughing for like 15 minutes solid. I swear, I couldn't do it again if I tried.
